d list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Account Manager requirements Bachelor's degree in communications or business Proficiency in Microsoft Excel Clear communication skills Ability to multitask Problem solving skills Attention to detail Account Manager related job titles: Senior Account Manager Junior Account Manager Account Executive Business Account Coordinator Account Representative Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
